:GRAPH Stock_vs_Flow
:TITLE Stock vs Flow
:X-AXIS Measured Flow
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Measured Stock

:GRAPH Stock_1st_Difference
:TITLE Stock 1st Difference
:X-AXIS Lagged Measured Flow
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Stock 1st Difference

:GRAPH Trend_Comparison
:TITLE Trend Comparison
:X-DIV 4
:SCALE
:VAR Flow Trend
:SCALE
:VAR Stock Trend
